Package: shiny.webawesome
Title: Shiny Bindings for Web Awesome Components
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("M. B.", "Anand", , "anand@owlcyberlabs.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an R and Shiny interface to the Web Awesome component
    library. The package is generator-driven, exposing Web Awesome web
    components as R functions that produce HTML tags and integrate with
    Shiny's reactive model.
